<div class="container product-page" id="top">
  <div class="title text-center">
    <h1>Record Breaker</h1>
    <hr />
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-4 product-image">
      <%= image_tag('recordbreaker.jpg', style: 'height: 300px;') %>
    </div>

    <div class="col-sm-8">
      <h2>Create New Records</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>2-Panel</li>
        <li>45 gram</li>
        <li>Sand filled</li>
      </ul>
      <%= link_to "Read more...", "#moreinfo" %>
      <hr />
      <div class="product-price">
        <p>$7.25</p>
      </div>
      <%= link_to "Buy Now!", "http://www.amazon.com/Its-Ridic-Record-breaker-2-panel-Footbag/dp/B013TN92MQ", class: "btn btn-primary" %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <hr />
  <div class="center-block">
    <h2 class="text-center">Product Review</h2>
    <iframe class="center-block" width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/K8FmRmGjoU8" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
  </div>
  <hr />
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-12 additional-information center-block">
      <h2 class="text-center"><i class="fa fa-info-circle" id="moreinfo"></i></h2>
      <h2 class="text-center">Additional Information</h2>
      <p>
        The It's Ridic! Record Breaker is an excellent all-around hack.  The 2-panel design allows for better stalling than hacks
        with a lot of panels.  The traditional sand filled hack gives this hack the perfect combination of pop and flight.
      </p>
      <h2 class="text-center"><i class="fa fa-support"></i></h2>
      <h2 class="text-center">Care Instructions</h2>
      <p>
        We recommend following <%= link_to "this video", "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Uxj_JfF4uQM" %> for washing instructions.
      </p>
      <h2 class="text-center"><i class="fa fa-question-circle"></i></h2>
      <h2 class="text-center">More Questions?</h2>
      <p>
        Shoot us an <%= link_to "email", "mailto:info@itsridic.com" %> or check out the <%= link_to "Amazon product page", "http://www.amazon.com/Its-Ridic-Record-breaker-2-panel-Footbag/dp/B013TN92MQ" %> where some questions (may) have already been answered.
      </p>
      <br />
      <p class="text-center">
        <%= link_to "<< Top >>", "#top" %>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

